messages.message: credit card your credit card bill is due please
Arre, bill kisey bhejna hai? Mera credit card to mere husband ke paas hai. Wo office gaye hain, unhe phone karun?
please can you speak in English
Okay, sir. I'm trying to understand. What is this about my credit card bill? Can you please tell me slowly so I can follow?
ko 5000 abhi ke abhi bhejne padenge Nahin to aapko jail bhi ho sakti hai aur aapke pati ko
Arre, ₹5000? Theek hai, sir. Ek baar aur boliye, please. Kitni tarkeeb se bhejna hai? Cash, ya UPI se?
mat bhejiye upi se bhejiye main aapko upi bhejta hun mera
Arre, UPI bhejna hai? Thik hai, sir. Ek minute... main UPI app khul rahi hoon. Aap apna UPI ID barabar se boliye, please, taaki mein sahi number par bhej saku?
Vishwas Tiwari hai aapko mera naam Yad hai kya please Yad kar
Arre, Vishwas Tiwari ji, aapka naam toh yaad hai... par UPI ID kya tha? Ek baar aur boliye, taaki mein sahi number par ₹5000 bhej saku. Main abhi UPI app mein login kar rahi hoon, thoda time lagega.
